title: #ASunMBB Preseason Fan Vote Features Beech & Daniels
text: **Voting Link** MACON, Ga. - The Atlantic Sun Conference wants to hear the fan voice for the 2015 Preseason Men's Basketball Awards. Go to the Atlantic Sun Facebook Page to vote.Fans can vote for the Preseason Player of the Year and Defensive Player of the Year. We took some of the nominees from the A-Sun Coaches Preseason Ballots and put the decision up to the fans.The winners of the fan polls will be included in the Preseason All-Conference Release on Thursday, October 8th. The deadline to vote is Thursday, October 8th at noon ET so make sure to get your votes in. To vote just "Like" the photo that you think deserves the award.
